Show PieHelper manual:less \"${PH_BASE_DIR}/HOWTO\" 2>/dev/null
Show PieHelper version:confpieh_ph.sh -g | more
Check PieHelper configuration:echo \"Quit PieHelper from the menu and run '${PH_SUDO} ${PH_SCRIPTS_DIR}/confpieh_ph.sh -v' to verify the current configuration\"
List modules:confpieh_ph.sh -p list -m prompt
Toggle module debug:confpieh_ph.sh -p debug -m prompt
Go to Main:ph_show_menu Main
Open a shell (Type 'CTRL-D' to return):cd;/bin/bash
Quit:break
Return to previous screen:return
